        "subject": "LU-9833 utils: Make format-truncation nonfatal",
        "message": "LU-9833 utils: Make format-truncation nonfatal\n\nWe have some warnings triggered with format-truncation that is on\nby default in newer gcc.\nI reviewed them, filed tickets where appropriate and believe the\nrest of them should be more or less harmless.\n\nSo now we'll leave the warnings i, but make them not fatal fo build.\n\nChange-Id: Iadebb996ea672ef110975dde6cf0d249728a7aca\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
